        <div xml:id="TK1317">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>vaḻuttiṉāḷ tummiṉē māka vaḻittaḻutāḷ </l>
<l> yāruḷḷit tummiṉī reṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>When I sneezed she blessed me, but at once changed (her mind) and wept, asking, "At the thought of whom did you sneeze?"</l>
            </lg>
